name: Athanatos Systems
body:
### **Welcome to Athanatos Systems**
We have many forms of entertainment including music, games, and other media that are crafted with human precision and utilize many aspiring game developers as well as growing music artists. 

### **Music**
Many up-and-coming music artists have helped create music for **AS** since its genesis.

### **Games**
Including links to popular games, you can find whatever game you wish to play by clicking on a link below.

- Addictinggames.com
- Albion Online
- Battlenet
- Runescape
- Steam games

### **Founder, Authors and Contributors**
Daniel Schultz (@Square-Oracle) founded Athanatos Systems in July 2016. Since then, he has had numerous contributors to his works.

### **Support or Contact**
